# PigeonLib Architecture

## Boot Sequence

```
main()  [EntryPoint.h]
  └── pg::CreateApplication()           (client-defined; registers app-specific systems)
        └── Application::Create()
              └── Init()
                    ├── Window::Create()               (platform window + graphics context)
                    ├── World::Create()                (ECS registry, clears all state)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(AudioPlaybackSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(AudioVolumeSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(CameraSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(ConfigLoaderSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(InputSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(ResourceManagerSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(TransformComposeSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(TransformResolveSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(UIControlSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(UIEventSystem)
                    ├── RegisterSystem(UIRenderSystem)
                    ├── Renderer::Init()               (RendererAPI, RenderCommand setup)
                    ├── PushOverlay(ImGuiLayer)         [non-test builds only]
                    └── m_Initialized = true
  └── app.Run()
```

## Per-Frame Update Sequence

```
UpdateApp()
  1. Clock::Restart()           → Timestep (inter-frame delta)
  2. LayerStack::Begin()        — ImGuiLayer opens a new Dear ImGui frame
  3. LayerStack::OnUpdate(ts)   — game layers receive delta-time
  4. World::Update(ts)          — see internal sequence below
  5. LayerStack::End()          — ImGuiLayer renders accumulated ImGui draw data
  6. Window::OnUpdate()         — drains OS message queue, then SwapBuffers
```

## World::Update Internal Sequence

```
World::Update(ts)
  ├── [first frame after RegisterSystem] SortSystems()
  │     └── Kahn topological sort; edges from writeSet/inframeAddSet → readSet
  ├── m_Dispatcher.update()       — EnTT signal delivery
  ├── for each system in sorted order:
  │     └── system->Update(ts)    — via CheckedRegistryAccessor
  ├── ClearEvents()               — destroys all entities tagged EventComponent
  └── FlushDeferredRequests()
        ├── apply m_DeferredOneFrameComponents  (emplace + schedule removal)
        ├── apply m_DeferredRequests            (persistent emplaces, removes)
        └── apply m_DeferredDestroys            (entity destruction)
```

## Platform Event Flow

```
Win32 WM_* message
  └── WindowsWindow::WindowProc
        └── Application::OnEvent(Event&)
              ├── Direct: WindowClose → m_Running=false
              ├── Direct: WindowResize → Renderer::OnWindowResize, m_Minimized flag
              └── World::EmplaceExternalEvent<XxxEventComponent>()
                    └── deferred entity: visible to ECS systems in the NEXT World::Update
```

## Module Interaction Map

```
Platform
  └── implements: Window, PlatformInput, GraphicsContext, RendererAPI, Buffer, Shader, Texture
                                │ (abstract interfaces only visible above this line)
                                ▼
Core
  ├── Application          boot sequence, layer stack, OS event bridge
  ├── ConfigLoaderSystem   Assets/Engine/Config.json (+ <savedataPath>/Config.json override)  →  EngineConfigSingletonComponent  (frame 1 only)
  ├── InputSystem          input event components  →  InputStateSingletonComponent
  └── ResourceManagerSystem  manifests  →  ResourceMapSingletonComponent  (frame 1 only)
                                │
                                ▼
Audio
  ├── AudioVolumeSystem    EngineConfigSingletonComponent (volumes) + SetAudioVolumeRequest
  │                          →  AudioVolumeSingletonComponent (live master/sound/music volumes)
  └── AudioPlaybackSystem  ResourceMapSingletonComponent (m_SoundMap) + AudioVolumeSingletonComponent
                             + Play/Stop/Pause/ResumeAudioRequest (from app)
                             →  AudioDeviceSingletonComponent (platform mixer); voices keyed by UUID handle

Transform
  ├── TransformResolveSystem  ResolvedTransformRequest (from app) + CameraTransformRequest
  │                           →  PositionComponent, RotationComponent, ScaleComponent, LocalBoundsComponent
  └── TransformComposeSystem  Position/Rotation/Scale/LocalBounds  →  WorldTransformComponent (matrix + sort key)
                                │ (render bridges read WorldTransformComponent)
                                ▼
Renderer
  ├── CameraSystem         KeyPressedEvent + ScrollEvent + ResizeEvent + PositionComponent
  │                          →  OrthographicCameraComponent + CameraTransformRequest (pan)
  └── Renderer2DSystem
        reads:  OrthographicCameraComponent, EngineConfigSingletonComponent,
                ResourceMapSingletonComponent, Draw*InFrameEvent
        writes: RendererDataSingletonComponent → GPU draw calls, world draws Y-sorted, UI on top
                                ▲
                                │ (emits DrawUI*InFrameEvent)
UI
  ├── UIControlSystem      mutation commands  →  BaseComponent, ImageComponent, TextComponent
  ├── UIEventSystem        InputStateSingletonComponent  →  UIOn*OneFrameComponent (hit-test results)
  └── UIRenderSystem       BaseComponent + ImageComponent/TextComponent
                             →  DrawUIQuadInFrameEvent, DrawUIStringInFrameEvent
```

## Key Files

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Core/Application.h` | Application singleton — window, layer stack, boot sequence |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Audio/` | Audio module — SoundClip resource, abstract AudioDevice mixer, the volume + playback systems, request components (see Documentation/ModuleInfo/Audio) |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Platform/Miniaudio/MiniaudioAudioDevice.cpp` | Real audio backend (miniaudio); Testing build uses Platform/Testing/TestingAudioDevice |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/Entity.h` | ECS abstraction layer — `pg::ecs` names (`Entity`, `null`, `Registry`, `Dispatcher`, `exclude`) over the EnTT library |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/World.h` | ECS World API — registry, system registration, deferred operations |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/CheckedRegistryAccessor.h` | Accessor API — View, Get, EmplaceDeferred, EmplaceInframe, EmplaceEvent |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/ECS/System.h` | Base System class and SystemAccessDecl struct |
| `Code/PigeonLib/Pigeon/Transform/` | Transform components (Position/Rotation/Scale/LocalBounds/WorldTransform), the resolve + compose systems, and the request types (ADR 0003) |
| `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox2D.cpp` | Entry point — CreateApplication() + client system registration |
